query:
SELECT at.id, at.templateName, aty.auditName, aty.templateReference, 
(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM auditTemplateSections WHERE auditTemplateId = at.id) as sectionCount,
(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM auditTemplateQuestions atq 
 JOIN auditTemplateSections ats ON atq.auditTemplateSectionId = ats.id 
 WHERE ats.auditTemplateId = at.id) as questionCount
FROM auditTemplates at
JOIN auditTypes aty ON at.auditTypeId = aty.id
WHERE aty.templateReference IN ('SUPER-001', 'RECRUIT-001', 'SEC-001')
ORDER BY aty.templateReference;
